snippet.title: REAL MADRID 5 - 1 REAL BETIS | RESUMEN LALIGA EA SPORTS
snippet.description:
Goleada del Real Madrid por 5-1 ante el Real Betis en el Santiago Bernabéu, en un encuentro marcado por la gran actuación de Gonzalo, autor de un hat-trick. El delantero abrió el marcador de cabeza en la primera parte y amplió la ventaja tras el descanso con un potente disparo desde la frontal. Raúl Asencio firmó el tercer tanto a balón parado antes de que Cucho Hernández recortara distancias para el Betis. En el tramo final, Gonzalo completó su triplete y Fran García cerró el marcador en el tiempo añadido. 

#RealMadridRealBetis LALIGA EA SPORTS 2025/26 J18

FAST & FURIOUS 11 (2026) becomes a global event — a battle for bloodline, loyalty, and the promise that family never falls.

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

The Odyssey - In Theaters 07.17.26

Christopher Nolan’s next film, The Odyssey, is a mythic action epic shot across the world using brand new IMAX® film technology. The film brings Homer’s foundational saga to IMAX® film screens for the first time and opens in theaters everywhere on July 17, 2026. 

The Odyssey stars Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, Robert Pattinson and Lupita Nyong’o, with Zendaya and Charlize Theron.

The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

When a dangerous new Kumite emerges with rules designed to break even the strongest fighters, old rivals become unlikely allies facing opponents who show no mercy. Fists fly, bones crack, and honor becomes the only currency that matters when stepping into a ring where walking out alive is never guaranteed.

snippet.title: ጫክ ጫካኮ||ዘማሪ ሞገስ አማኑኤል Caakki Caakakkoo New Song Moges Amanuel 2026
snippet.description:
ጫክ ጫካኮ ኡል ሁንዲና 2×.
ተንስ ጠኖዮ አመዴና 2×
  ሃሬች መን እንካሞ ኢየሱሳ ኤዴና
  ሁንድም መት አን ኦሶ ከኖ ሊራሞና
ኤ ቱንስ ዶሌ ህንጋሞ ጫከኔ ፍላሞ
ኢትኔ ዶሉካንና እልል ይኖሞ
    እልል ንዋዕና
    እልል ኢየሱስና 
    ፈዬናሞ ባጢዕል ጀብስ 2×
    ፍሉሞቴ ኬዕማል ቱንስ 2×
  
1) ባጢል ከራ ሄኑም ምናደባ 
     ብዕኖም ኡል ጢግኔ ሲዳ ኤባ 
     አድለኔካ ቄሶመኔካ 
     ኤዴሱኮ ኤ ኢመን ላከ
        ኮይ ሄኑም ኔሴ ኦስ እሳኮ
         ካዕሰም ኢታ ገትሳኮ 
        ሌህካ መላዬ እቃምሳኮ
        ሊራሞና ዶል ዋራኮ


2.እጥ  ኮሎ ሂንጭኔና ገዳኣ ሲንዳ
   አነናጥ ጎርተና ሌህኔ ግንዳ
  ሀዊክ አጠቂ ሀንሴ ድላ
  ሄሽኑም ዶሌ ጢግኔ ጉላ 
     መሶኦም ቤኤ መት አን ኦሶ
     ማሴአማ ጎጊ አን ቤዮ መሶ 
     ሃሬች መና ከባ ኔስ
     ሁንደም ሲዳኮ ኢየሱስ
     ሁንደም ሙጩሳ ኢየሱስ 

3)ዋዕ አድለን አናን እንካ
  ኡረቶ ሲንዶኔ ሄኑሞካ
  አነናቶ ቢዕሳ ለምቤዕካ
አረሱኮ ኢየሱስ ን ቤዮ ቢካ 
     ጡማ አለላታ መንሁንድና
     ጡፈማ ፎቃኣ እጦ ሞዕኖና
     እታንሳኮ ዋዕ ጌሬች 
     ኦኮ ፍራኮ ጡም ኤልንች

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. snippet.title: I Beat Minecraft From ONLY BEDROCK
snippet.description:
I Beat Minecraft in a world that's COMPLETELY BEDROCK SUPERFLAT. This took over 2 months to record (mostly from overnight AFKing for pigs and wadnering traders lol) and about another month to edit. Although I got a lot of the editing done while AFKing in the world.

NOTE: so far no one has, but you may have noticed at the end of the video my spawn point or world spawn is in the pig farm, even though earlier it was where the snow is. This is because when trying to spawn pigs earlier I did a ton of experiments and I thought one of the problems was my world just couldn't spawn passive mobs, so I copied the world's blocks over to a new world as a solution. This changed the spawnpoint as I didn't paste the blocks in the perfect same spot coordinate wise as the original world. However I wasn't even right and it ended up just being bunnies stopping pigs from spawning 😂
